data.description: Introducing a prime investment in Brockton! a well-maintained 3-family multi-unit. Unit 1 & 2 offers 3 Bedrooms with 1 Bath with ample living space and Unit 3 consist of 2 Bedrooms and 1 Bath along with living and dining space, ensuring tenant comfort and consistent rental income, Paved driveway can safely accommodate 2-3 cars. With its strategic location this property promises both cash flow and future value. Don't miss out! Selling AS-IS.
